OL,3,CThousands evacuated across Europe as
OL,4,Cwildfires rage in France, Italy and
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FRed heat alerts remain in place across
OL,8,FSpain as wildfires burn across the
OL,9,Fcountry. Credit: APTN
OL,11,FEmergency services across Europe are
OL,12,Fcontinuing to fight wildfires as a
OL,13,Fheatwave sweeps across the
OL,14,FMediterranean, bringing scorching
OL,15,Ftemperatures.
OL,17,FOn Thursday, huge wildfires were still
OL,18,Fburning thousands of hectares across
OL,19,FItaly, France and Spain, as
OL,20,Ftemperatures in Sicily reached 49C
OL,21,Fthis week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
