PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784845107
OL,3,CThousands evacuated across Europe as
OL,4,Cwildfires rage in France, Italy and
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FSpain's meteorological agency AEMET
OL,8,Fhas also warned of "extraordinary
OL,9,Fdanger", with forecasters predicting
OL,10,Fhighs of 44C - approaching the
OL,11,Fnation's 47.6C heat record from five
OL,12,Fyears ago.
OL,14,FITV News takes a closer look.
OL,16,FDangerous red heat alerts have been
OL,17,Fissued across south-eastern Spain,
OL,18,Fwith Valle del Almanzora and Almeria
OL,19,Fexpected to hit more than 44C on
OL,20,FThursday.
