OL,3,CThousands evacuated across Europe as
OL,4,Cwildfires rage in France, Italy and
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FMore than 32,000 hectares have been
OL,8,Fburnt in Guadalajara, central Spain,
OL,9,Fas the country's second largest
OL,10,Fwildfire or record, continues to blaze
OL,11,Fafter nearly a week.
OL,13,FPeople were evacuated from 34
OL,14,Fvillages, and local authorities said
OL,15,Fwater-dropping aircrafts have managed
OL,16,Fto protect homes from burning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
