OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784845107
OL,3,CThousands evacuated across Europe as
OL,4,Cwildfires rage in France, Italy and
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FEmiliano Garcia-Page, regional
OL,8,Fpresident of Castilla La Mancha, about
OL,9,F106 miles south of Madrid, said
OL,10,Ffirefighters hope to have the wildfire
OL,11,Funder control by Friday.
OL,13,FMiguel Angel Moreno, a local mayor of
OL,14,Fone of the evacuated villages, said
OL,15,Fsome residents had taken refuge at a
OL,16,FRed Cross shelter.
OL,18,FHe described firefighters tackling the
OL,19,Fblaze as unnamed heroes who deserve as
OL,20,Fmuch admiration as the World Cup
OL,21,Fwinners.
