OL,3,CThousands evacuated across Europe as
OL,4,Cwildfires rage in France, Italy and
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FIn Leon, northern Spain, two
OL,8,Flocalities have been evacuated as
OL,9,Femergency services battle a forest
OL,10,Ffire, Spanish police said.
OL,12,FAlmost 12,000 people were evacuated on
OL,13,FWednesday night as a wildfire burned
OL,14,Fin Le Porge, west of Bordeaux.
OL,16,F500 firefighters tackled the blaze,
OL,17,Fwhich covered at least 2,000 hectares,
OL,18,Fbut no one has been injured, local
OL,19,Fauthorities confirmed.
