OL,3,CThousands evacuated across Europe as
OL,4,Cwildfires rage in France, Italy and
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FDrone footage captures fire scorching
OL,8,Facross the Bordeaux region in
OL,9,Fsouthwest France
OL,11,FCredit: Alice Al, EBU
OL,13,FTourists staying at eight holiday
OL,14,Fcamps in the region were among those
OL,15,Fforced to leave.
OL,17,FThe French government said the
OL,18,Fsituation remains "unfavourable".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
