OL,3,CThousands evacuated across Europe as
OL,4,Cwildfires rage in France, Italy and
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FInterior minister Laurent Nunez said
OL,8,FFrance has already seen more than
OL,9,F12,500 wildfires since the beginning
OL,10,Fof the year, with almost 44,000
OL,11,Fhectares burned.
