OL,3,CThousands evacuated across Europe as
OL,4,Cwildfires rage in France, Italy and
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FFirefighters in Sicily have carried
OL,8,Fout more than 1,000 wildfire
OL,9,Foperations since Saturday and have
OL,10,Fworked double shifts in an attempt to
OL,11,Fbattle the blazes.
OL,13,FThe Italian fire brigade and minister
OL,14,FMatteo Piantedosi shared their
OL,15,Fcondolences on Wednesday after a
OL,16,Ffirefighter died trying to extinguish
OL,17,Fa wildfire in San Cataldo.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
