OL,3,CThousands evacuated across Europe as
OL,4,Cwildfires rage in France, Italy and
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FEmergency services have also been put
OL,8,Funder strain as temperatures in
OL,9,FPalermo soared to 49C and didn't fall
OL,10,Fbelow 30C in the evening.
OL,12,FWind has fuelled the flames, turning
OL,13,Fland to ash and threatening homes and
OL,14,Fbusinesses.
OL,16,FElsewhere, in Santo Stefano Quisquina,
OL,17,Fat least 100 people were evacuated in
OL,18,Fdue to a large fire near the town
OL,19,Fcentre on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
