OL,3,CThousands evacuated across Europe as
OL,4,Cwildfires rage in France, Italy and
OL,5,CSpain
OL,7,FIn Calabria, southern Italy, fires
OL,8,Fcontinue to burn as authorities probe
OL,9,Finvestigations into suspected arson.
OL,11,FDomenico Costarella, who works for
OL,12,FCalabria's Civil Protection Agency
OL,13,Fsaid cats with "flammable-soaked rags
OL,14,Ftied to their tails" were seen
OL,15,F"running around and spreading the
OL,16,Ffire".
OL,18,FIt is not the first time cats have
OL,19,Fbeen used to start fires, as
OL,20,Fauthorities in Sicily reported
OL,21,Fincident in a national park in 2016.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
